verbose_text: In contrast to the beta agonist, the alpha 1 -agonist (10-50 muM) phenylephrine (PE) partially mimicked the Epi effect and increased spontaneous AP discharge in 66% (6/9 cells) of NA cells (XREF_FIG), whereas it was without effect in the remainder.
evidence: alpha 1 -agonist (10-50 muM) phenylephrine (PE) partially mimicked the Epi effect and increased spontaneous AP
